="background-color:#489148"><div class="ly9QplHZA_LvOzPYiHNI"></div><picture><source srcSet="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/508787285/tr/foto%C4%9Fraf/landscape.jpg?s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=lBv-TYCBJDQZ9awJw6BdMqIHcJm5JSxMoJQWzRJc1yE="/><img class="_BZ9oiIzKJoKWjkJDof_" src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/508787285/tr/foto%C4%9Fraf/landscape.jpg?s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=lBv-TYCBJDQZ9awJw6BdMqIHcJm5JSxMoJQWzRJc1yE=" alt="landscape - adapazari stok fotoğraflar ve resimler" width="612" height="459" loading="lazy"/></picture><figcaption class="ck6ZnqfY1sJEhiekEium">landscape - adapazari stok fotoğraflar ve resimler</figcaption></figure></a><div class="n34m6eYtJQfW1ZwAjlBW"><div class="EFdbEQFdcN1016EBDOlB" data-testid="gateway-asset-title"><a href="/tr/foto%C4%9Fraf/landscape-gm508787285-45614148">Landscape</a></div></div></article></div></div><div class="vnBlOzAX1i2xs1n1TAo1" style="--width:612;--height:408"><div class="
